name: Above The Sea 7 Summits
description:
7 highest mountains in 7 continents around the world, where are not many people can conquer them all.
Mount Everest 8,848.86 m. (Asia)
Mount Aconcagua 6,961 m. (South America)
Mount Denali 6,190 m. (North America)
Mount Kilimanjaro 5,895 m. (Africa)
Mount Elbrus 5,642 m. (Europe)
Mount Vinson Massif 4,892 m. (Antarctica)
Mount Puncak Jaya 4,884 m. (Australia /Oceanea)
